.
</emphasis>
Wings slightly rubbed, left antenna broken. 
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF8BFFC1E85443F8B0BAF816" bold="true" box="[1101,1273,1973,1998]" pageId="17" pageNumber="522">
<typeStatus id="54B4E7F8FF8BFFC1E85443F8B0B7F816" box="[1101,1268,1973,1998]" pageId="17" pageNumber="522">Paralectotype</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Right antenna missing. Left hindwing with a slight damage near the internal margin.
</paragraph>
